org.openhubframework.openhub.component.funnel

Class MsgFunnelComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.camel.support.ServiceSupport
      • org.apache.camel.impl.DefaultComponent
        • org.openhubframework.openhub.component.funnel.MsgFunnelComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CamelContextAware, Component, Service, ShutdownableService, StatefulService, SuspendableService

    public class MsgFunnelComponent
extends DefaultComponent
    Apache Camel component "msg-funnel" for filtering processing messages. This component ensures that there is only one processing message with same funnel value.

    Syntax: msg-funnel:default[?options] where options are

    • idleInterval - Interval (in seconds) that determines how long can be message processing.
    • guaranteedOrder - if funnel component should guaranteed order of processing messages
    • excludeFailedState - if FAILED state should be involved in guaranteed order
    • id - funnel component identifier

    Valid for asynchronous messages only.

    Author:
    Petr Juza
